name: Love Spike Necklace
description:
Love spike pendant made with solid brass and plated in 14k gold. 

This pendant's design was personally hand carved out of wax in my home studio and casted at a local metalsmith in downtown Los Angeles' jewelry district. Finished polishing and chain attached by hand.

This piece is part of my debut 'Heartbreaker' collection, combining edgy, funky, and rock chic styles.

I hope you enjoy it!

-16" gold plated chain
- 1"pendant width
-" 1.4"pendant length
